  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Food to help hungry children stay awake at school</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Malnutrition and poverty in Burundi has recently been made even worse by COVID-19. Food prices have doubled and travel restrictions have made it impossible to gather basic supplies. Children are falling asleep at school after the 4km walk having had nothing to eat for days. This project will feed 250 children every day for 6 months in addition to starting up a kitchen garden to enable them to become self-sustaining. Let&apos;s help our children now so they can feed future generations.</narrative>
  </description>
